    |-config.py
    |-manage.py
-----------------------------------------
usage:
	python manage.py
-----------------------------------------
base funciton:
search blank: search for the blog based on the keywords
explore: the recently published blog
Home: write your blog
Blog: to show all the Blog and your friends blog
Comment:write your comment
----------------------------------------
the navigation bar:
Flasky:to get the post your friend publish
Blog:to write your own blog
Explore: provide search and I'm feeling something
userInfo: the show the information and log in,log out
----------------------------------------
to get requirements:   pip freeze > requirements.txt
to install dependency: pip install -r requirements.txt
